000015EE                           767  * Section       : Delta Time
000015EE                           768  * Description   : For slowing down runtime, make it consistent.
000015EE                           769  *-----------------------------------------------------------
000015EE                           770  LAST_TIME       DS.L    1       ; milliseconds elapsed lsat cycle
000015F2                           771  CURRENT_TIME    DS.L    1       ; milliseconds passed since last cycle
000015F6                           772  DELTA_TIME      DS.L    1       ; multiply any velocity with this to make movement over time consistent.
